title: Wenjun
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Local eatery serving mostly vegetarian food with various Jianshui specialties like grilled tofu, noodle dishes, desserts, pickles. Food is very spicy. Directions: from Li'nan road (the main tourist street), reach Temple of Tianjun, go down the small lane almost opposite the temple, perpendicular to Lin'an Road, walk 200 meters till you reach the end of this lane, and the eatery is to your right, on the corner.
